<h1>Game Instructions</h1>

<!-- Introduction paragraph providing an overview of the game and its goals -->
<p>Welcome to the <strong>Purgatory Dungeon Crawl</strong>! In this game, you must navigate through a perilous dungeon filled with enemies, traps, and treasures. Your goal is to make your way from one corner of the map to the other while battling foes, collecting weapons, and surviving the dangers that await. Follow the instructions below to get started!</p>

<h2>Controls</h2>
<!-- Lists the controls used to navigate the dungeon -->
<ul>
    <li><strong>W</strong> - Move up</li>
    <li><strong>A</strong> - Move left</li>
    <li><strong>S</strong> - Move down</li>
    <li><strong>D</strong> - Move right</li>
</ul>

<h2>Objective</h2>
<!-- Explains the main objective of the game -->
<p>Your starting point is in the top-left corner of the map, and your goal is to make it to the bottom-right corner. Along the way, you'll face enemies, pick up weapons, and manage your health. Stay alert, as the dungeon holds many surprises!</p>

<h2>Map Tiles</h2>
<!-- Describes the functionality of different map tiles -->
<ul>
    <li><strong>Red tiles:</strong> These are walls that block your path. You cannot pass through them.</li>
    <li><strong>Blue tiles:</strong> These are walkable spaces where you can move freely. Explore them to find treasures, enemies, and potions.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Weapons</h2>
<!-- Explains how players interact with and upgrade weapons -->
<p>Throughout the dungeon, you'll come across a variety of weapons. You can pick up stronger weapons automatically when you move over them, but weaker weapons will be left behind. Choose your path carefully and make sure to upgrade your weaponry to face tougher enemies!</p>

<h2>Combat</h2>
<!-- Outlines the automatic combat system and its mechanics -->
<p>Combat in <strong>Purgatory</strong> is handled automatically. When you encounter an enemy, your character will engage in battle, with the outcome displayed on-screen. The strength of your weapon and the health of both you and your enemies will determine the battle's result. Be prepared for tough fights!</p>

<h2>Health</h2>
<!-- Provides information about health mechanics and items -->
<p>Your health is crucial for survival. It will not regenerate over time. However, if you come across a <strong>Healing Potion</strong>, it will restore your health. Keep an eye out for these precious items, as they may be your only way to survive longer battles!</p>

<h2>Tips for Success</h2>
<!-- Offers helpful tips for players to succeed in the game -->
<ul>
    <li>Explore every corner of the dungeon to find valuable weapons and potions.</li>
    <li>Pay attention to the color of tiles—avoid walls and keep track of your movement options.</li>
    <li>Keep your health up by collecting healing potions whenever you can.</li>
    <li>Upgrade your weapons to increase your chances of surviving enemy encounters.</li>
</ul>

<p>Good luck, adventurer! The dungeon awaits you...</p>
